=Description=

"The classroom can be fundamentally improved. Teachers currently spend valuable class time lecturing information to their students. We want to end the lecture and give teachers more time in class to actually engage with their students, and not simply address them.

We're building OPEN, a free tool used by teachers to create digital lessons for their own students. Instead of learning content in the classroom, students will take lessons created by their own teacher at home and spend the class period working on homework-style problems."


